/22/owatashi2.jpg\"><img alt=\"owatashi2.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/03/owatashi2-thumb-450xauto-6189.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><br><a href=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/img/2014/03/22/owatashi3.jpg\"><img alt=\"owatashi3.jpg\" src=\"http://img.nogizaka46.com/blog/staff/assets_c/2014/03/owatashi3-thumb-450xauto-6191.jpg\" width=\"450\" class=\"mt-image-none\"></a></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><br><br></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"></p>\t\t</div>","transTitle":"《乃木坂和物语》交货会报告","url":"http://blog.nogizaka46.com/staff/smph/2014/03/017453.php"}